description: Demolition of all existing buildings and construction of 4 buildings ranging from 9 to 16 storeys in height, comprising 162 residential units; office (B1) accommodation; drinking establishment (A4); flexible workspace/non-residential institution (B1/D1) use; flexible retail (A1/A2/A3) uses; car and cycle parking, servicing, refuse and associated plant; public realm improvements incidental to the development including the creation of a level threshold fronting Battersea Park Road and a new public route through the centre of the site; hard and soft landscaping works; infrastructure works and other associated works  An Environmental Statement has been submitted with the application under the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2011 (As amended) (Amended Description)
